=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪玩啦，你開住緊部機唔係用緊電？<br />\n姐係叉滿左自己 cut 電啦...唔再叉...<br />\n咁99.9%佢自己會唔會又再叉返？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n傻仔衝出黎柒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n衝出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n滿左電之後會直接係socket度攞電呀柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"215e1ba92af1e01ab09edf24fdb0d44585277577","tid":34361,"uid":33831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:41:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正確做法叉到滿之後平時可以叉住用，佢會自己轉用濕電，咁就唔會到用粒電，不過每過一段時間都要深度叉電<br />\n<br />\n點為之深度？用電用到40%樓下，再一下叉爆佢，中途唔好邊叉邊用<br />\n<br />\n忌：<br />\n邊叉邊用（非100%）<br />\n長時間唔用電池<br />\n用電用到耗盡而熄機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有野來問下<br />\n平時叉電個陣火牛都幾熱下<br />\n100%叉住用個陣(較左叉爆用火牛)<br />\n又只係少少暖<br />\n呢個情況係咪真係用緊火牛架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c214c158f7905dcabdc782d1b66a792e074dd0","tid":34361,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:48:04.000Z","msg":"MacBook 好似係火牛直接攞電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除非你個software太勁 好似premium 嗰啲先會用埋你舊電啲電 所以正常應該插住用 好似係"},{"pid":"b193e3b32794ea7b02ab5cbb8430ae78fc72e6ef","tid":34361,"uid":2438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:50:48.000Z","msg":"問得呢個問題就用返win機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8a023ec83b65efcc5fbf93092a358eaca97890","tid":34361,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:57:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪玩啦，而家廿一世紀㕸，邊有野差滿唔識自己cut電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪玩啦，你開住緊部機唔係用緊電？<br />\n姐係叉滿左自己 cut 電啦...唔再叉...<br />\n咁99.9%佢自己會唔會又再叉返？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n傻仔衝出黎柒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad